data.text:
Neetho Cheppana

Music : Mani Sharma

Lyricist : Sirivennala Sitaramasastri

Singers : S P Balu, Chitra

Lyrics:

[Female]

neetho cheppana neekuda thelisina

nuvventhaga rechipothe antha sarada thelusuna

[Male]

garam chesina nayagaram chupina

kanikarame kaluguthondhe kashtapadake kanchana

[Female]

neneee nenuga leneee lenuga a a a a

[Male]

naa kannulaaa needhee vennela o o o

[Female]

neetho cheppana neekuda thelisina

nuvventhaga rechipothe antha sarada thelusuna

[Female]

inkoncham anukuna ikachalle anana

vadalamante emitardham vadhili pommanaa

[Male]

panimala paipaina padathavem pasikoona

muddhu meeruthunna pantham haddhulone aapana

[Female]

maghuva manasu thelisena magajathiki

[Male]

mogali monalu thagilena letha soyagaaniki kootha deniki

garam chesina nayagaram chupina

kanikarame kaluguthondhe kashtapadake kanchana

[Male]

vodhigunna voralona kadhilinchake kurradhana

katthi samutho pramadham pattu jarena

[Female]

pedhavopani padhuneena paravaledhanukona

kottha premalo vinodham neekhu nenu nerpana

[Male]

sontha sogasu baruvena sukumariki

[Female]

antha berusu paruvena rakumarudanti ni rajasaniki
